    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Planes used in conjunction with a set of handrail planes; the former cuts the top of the handrail and the latter cuts the sides.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
